OL,3,CHealth officials to meet P&O cruise
OL,4,Cafter 'gastrointestinal' illness
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FCruise passengers on a ship that left
OL,8,FSouthampton are having to isolate
OL,9,Fafter an illness broke out on board.
OL,11,FA number of people have suffered a
OL,12,Fstomach bug on P&O Cruises Ventura.
OL,14,FThe vessel, which has a capacity for
OL,15,F3,200 passengers, set off from
OL,16,FSouthampton on Saturday 11th May on a
OL,17,Ftwo-week trip around the Canary
OL,18,FIslands.
