OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FA spokesperson for P&O Cruises said,
OL,8,F"Ventura left Southampton on May 11,
OL,9,F2024 for a 14 night cruise around the
OL,10,FCanary Islands.
OL,12,F"Upon embarkation all guests were
OL,13,Fprovided with an advisory notice with
OL,14,Fprecautionary health measures for on
OL,15,Fboard and on shore, as is standard
OL,16,Fprocedure across our fleet.
OL,18,F"P&O Cruises swiftly implemented
OL,19,Fapproved and enhanced sanitisation
OL,20,Fprotocols to uphold the welfare of
OL,21,Feveryone onboard.
